title: Alshawn Martin on 6ix9ine Snitching, Unfollowing AD, Wyclef & More
description:
Alshawn Martin aka Hai Shawn Martin, has changed his name to reconcile with his Haitian roots, He talks about his come up, being on a positive path, relationships with 6ix9ine, Rick Ross, Wyclef and more! https://www.instagram.com/haishawnmar...

-----
00:00 Intro
1:00 T-Rell wanna know why everyone is dissing Alshawn
5:37 Adam comes in + Alshawn sounds like Flakko
7:47 AD distanced himself from Alshawn coz he was with 6ix9ine, AD turned down a feature, and Alshawn unfollowed AD
11:40 Alshawn says he’s the first to do a song with Fivio, and did the biggest tour drive in his hood for the kids, Wyclef gave him money, says his own ppl took it for granted and never said thanks
14:00 Alshawn linked up with 6ix9ine recently, still friends, T-Rell ain't havin it!
16:46 Alshawn gets emotional saying 6ix9ine changed his life
18:48 Says he made sure that none of his homies were involved with anything 6ix9ine had going on that led to the indictment
20:02 Alshawn always made sure 6ix9ine was straight in LA: "Dudes wasn't looking for us like that, that's some internet sh*t"
23:19 Joe Moses called Alshawn to see how close he was with 6ix9ine, he didn’t have to check in if he was with Alshawn but Moses gave him a hard time, then blocked Alshawn on socials
37:00 T-Rell used to be outside, ready to d*e for his homies, and realized none of them was willing to do the same
39:00 Alshawn's mom was m*rd*red in LA when she was 18, hangin out w the wrong people
40:29 Randomly meeting the Police officer lady who got her job from Alshawn mom's case
44:00 Tapin in with his Haitian culture going to New York through Wyclef, changed his name to Hay Shawn Martin
46:55 Friendship with Rick Ross plus introduces his promoter agency
48:34 Defends Rick Ross on the Birdman persona accusations
54:25 Alshawn says T-Rell is good at everything
55:15 Alshawn says AD is better lyrically tho lol
56:53 Alshawn says he stole his Traw “roar” from Tuff
1:06:33 Working with his twin Waka Floka
1:09:13 Alshawn calls out people who just come on No Jumper and just say anything, specifically Sharky on T-Rell's podcast said some things about Alshawn + Answers Treyway6k
1:16:00 Prayer
1:17:22 A.P.U.U support for gang members who wanna change their lives, and overcome immature decisions
